    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and maintained over the years. It runs super smoothly and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fresh adventures! It's the perfect choice if you're looking for something reliable that still looks great parked in the driveway. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
