    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative measures; the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings were recently addressed to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering the precise turn-in and lateral stability this chassis is known for. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain and chassis are optimized for immediate performance use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
