    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that balances performance with daily utility. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the bolsters on the driver\u2019s seat show light entry wear, but the upholstery remains free of tears or punctures. All onboard technology, including the navigation system and dual-zone climate control, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014the engine idles smoothly, the transmission provides crisp shifts, and there are no known fluid leaks. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection and an oil change, with the brake pads and tires showing significant life remaining. This is a dependable, honest car that presents beautifully and is ready for the road.",
